{"tid":1057352,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【技術文】點樣解凍D凍肉最好？","createTime":"2019-03-11T23:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T04:13:02.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94a896d4d7f02f5bc270f116bf0e3eba1e8975f6","tid":1057352,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:27:35.000Z","msg":"據新國華肉食公司老闆Dee哥多年經驗及實測，<br />\n<br />\n最佳的解凍方法是是用水沖浸，<br />\n其次是放在雪櫃解凍，<br />\n然後是放在鐵或鋁製品上解凍，<br />\n最後是置於室溫解凍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用水沖浸的好處是解凍速度最快，血水滲出最少；<br />\n<br />\n在雪櫃解凍雖然較慢，但能保持凍肉最佳溫度；<br />\n<br />\n鐵或鋁製品因為導熱快，相對解凍速度較快，缺點是血水會快速滲出，令肉色變得暗啞，影響賣相；<br />\n<br />\n而室溫解凍雖然解凍速度快，但血水會大量滲出，加上室溫易滋生細菌極不衞生，此為最不建議使用。"},{"pid":"53184117fee59875bb6715c2a688c41d648fc31d","tid":1057352,"uid":226587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:30:53.000Z","msg":"微波爐？"},{"pid":"b51fa6581d9bac764756db9735ce33fa3e475dfd","tid":1057352,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>微波爐？</blockquote><br />\n應該無乜人用掛&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;叮完出黎乾架喎"},{"pid":"41b7acf6ba7a63fb76e37a7b0cb68ca6504f7550","tid":1057352,"uid":3272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:46:11.000Z","msg":"召喚牛扒大師蚊蚊蚊"},{"pid":"a495a9a8cb8088204941ebc82895d96b30e9710f","tid":1057352,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:47:29.000Z","msg":"直接放入凍水煲，水滾熄火浸多兩分鐘就得"},{"pid":"be5b2fb53fe03885b44c51c2cd4e4c7a33f713d8","tid":1057352,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a495a9a8cb8088204941ebc82895d96b30e9710f","tid":1057352,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T23:47:29.000Z","msg":"直接放入凍水煲，水滾熄火浸多兩分鐘就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T00:22:56.000Z","msg":"而家叫你解凍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b19dc732e8112198e56e6bfd7452c53fed098e","tid":1057352,"uid":175943,"like":0,"dislik